{"type":null,"faqId":7814,"title":"华为荣耀如何使用DLNA？","answer":"DLNA(Digital Living Network Alliance)即数字生活网络联盟,为用户提供了方便快捷的媒体文件共享平台。DLNA主要功能有：<br />\n1、共享本地文件;<br />\n2、查看并播放本机或其他设备中共享的媒体文件；<br />\n3、向其他设备播放媒体文件；<br />\n4、向服务器上传媒体文件；<br />\n5、下载媒体文件。<br />\n首先，应将共享文件的设备应该都具有DLNA功能。所有设备全部连接到同一个WIFI网内，如同一个路由器或同一个热点。然后将各个设备的DLNA打开<br />","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":2,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7954","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1343443272000,"seriesProductName":"H60-L01,H60-L02,H60-L11,H60-L12","visitedTimes":3110,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":56,"times":18,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.1,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}